  "title": "Sales & Marketing Trainee [BIG ENERGY, BIG RESULTS]",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>✨ Sales & Marketing Trainee (Entry Level) ✨</strong></em></p><p>Ascend Marketing Solutions is on the hunt for hungry, driven self-starters who want more than a “normal” job. This is a performance-based sales & marketing role with uncapped earnings, fast-track career progression, and real leadership opportunities. You’ll be front-facing, repping premium brands, and learning how high-growth sales teams actually win. No fluff, just results.</p><p><u>Requirements</u></p><p>You bring the energy, confidence, and competitive mindset. If you’re a strong communicator, coachable, and motivated to grow fast, we want you. Sales, marketing, or customer-facing experience is a bonus but mindset, discipline, and drive matter more. If you’re ready to grind, grow, and get rewarded for it, this role is for you.</p>",
